source_schema.create_sql:
CREATE TABLE enterprise_logs (
                        id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
                        filename TEXT NOT NULL,
                        original_path TEXT NOT NULL,
                        archive_path TEXT,
                        file_hash TEXT NOT NULL,
                        file_size INTEGER NOT NULL,
                        created_date TEXT NOT NULL,
                        archived_date TEXT,
                        log_type TEXT,
                        status TEXT DEFAULT 'active',
                        metadata TEXT,
                        UNIQUE(filename, original_path)
                    )

target_schema.create_sql:
CREATE TABLE enterprise_logs (
                        log_id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,
                        doc_type TEXT DEFAULT 'LOG',
                        title TEXT NOT NULL,
                        content TEXT,
                        source_path TEXT,
                        last_updated TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
                        version TEXT,
                        hash_signature TEXT UNIQUE,
                        enterprise_compliance BOOLEAN DEFAULT 1,
                        quantum_indexed BOOLEAN DEFAULT 0,
                        category TEXT,
                        priority INTEGER DEFAULT 5,
                        status TEXT DEFAULT 'ACTIVE',
                        log_level TEXT DEFAULT 'INFO',
                        component TEXT,
                        session_id TEXT,
                        execution_phase TEXT,
                        error_count INTEGER DEFAULT 0,
                        warning_count INTEGER DEFAULT 0,
                        file_size INTEGER,
                        compression_ratio REAL,
                        archival_date TIMESTAMP,
                        retention_policy TEXT DEFAULT 'STANDARD'
                    )
